'''铬酸铬'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为Cr<sub>2</sub>(CrO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>，是Cr<sup>3+</sup>的[[铬酸盐|铬酸盐]]。

==化学性质==
铬酸铬在200℃之前都是稳定的。350℃时开始分解，产物有[[重铬酸铬|重铬酸铬]]、[[三氧化二铬|三氧化二铬]]和[[氧气|氧气]]：<ref>NE Fouad, SA Halawy, MA Mohamed, ''et al''.[https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Mohamed_Zaki5/publication/236162538_Thermal_and_spectroscopic_studies_of_chromium_chromate_hexahydrate_-A_likely_composition_for_redox_surfaces_of_calcined_chromia_catalysts/links/02e7e516987a25b570000000.pdf Thermal and spectroscopic studies of chromium chromate hexahydrate – a likely composition for redox surfaces of calcined chromia catalysts] {{Wayback|url=https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Mohamed_Zaki5/publication/236162538_Thermal_and_spectroscopic_studies_of_chromium_chromate_hexahydrate_-A_likely_composition_for_redox_surfaces_of_calcined_chromia_catalysts/links/02e7e516987a25b570000000.pdf |date=20190701191101 }}. ''Thermochimica Acta'', 1999. 329(1): 23-29. doi: 10.1016/S0040-6031(98)00658-3</ref>
: 2 Cr<sub>2</sub>(CrO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub> → Cr<sub>2</sub>(Cr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>)<sub>3</sub> + 2 Cr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> + 2 O<sub>2</sub>↑
它也可以被氢气还原为Cr<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>。
